    • Uses of RTSimulatorI in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.simulators

      Classes in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.simulators that implement RTSimulatorI 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  HIOA_AtomicRTEngine
      The class HIOA_AtomicRTEngine implements a simulation engine for HIOA atomic models which performs simulation in real time aka. the simulation clock follows the real physical time, eventually accelerated (or decelerated).

    • Uses of RTSimulatorI in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AtomicRTEngine
      The class AtomicRTEngine implements a simulation engine which performs simulation in real time aka. the simulation clock follows the real physical time, eventually accelerated (or decelerated).
      class  CoordinationRTEngine
      The class CoordinationRTEngine implements a real coordination engine.

    • Uses of RTSimulatorI in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators.interfaces

      Subinterfaces of RTSimulatorI in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.simulators.interfaces 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  RTAtomicSimulatorI
      The class RTAtomicSimulatorI defines the core behaviour of atomic simulation engines that execute models using the physical clock (of the underlying computer) as simulation clock, or a linear transformation of it (to simulate either faster or slower than the real physical time).
